{"tid":529014,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解BA仔dse高分過理科人 但係畢業出黎待遇差過狗？","createTime":"2018-01-14T12:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T17:46:01.000Z","uid":103616,"like":6,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"62b40170c7d6b3380e03106c945fe43244091383","tid":529014,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"因為on9 dse制度必修科三文一理<br />\n搞到班唔識用邏輯思考 淨係識吹水同背書嘅on9學生入曬大學<br />\n有邏輯思考 但係唔識吹水同擦老師鞋搏sba高分嘅理科生啲分俾人禁低曬<br />\n<br />\n但係而家呢個社會 需要有邏輯嘅人多過識吹水嘅人<br />\n有邏輯嘅人做乜工都得<br />\n但係淨係識吹水嘅垃圾就只可以做政客 做譁眾取寵嘅人<br />\n<br />\n希望政府早日改革dse制度 將STEM代替on9通識科做必修科<br />\n篩走啲淨係識吹水嘅垃圾出大學門外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53949c8f5f3257e8275cce83f24d1e857f0fc4a7","tid":529014,"uid":7837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"9ac4b35afa735070ddd1cf4ab8815553848f8e04","tid":529014,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:38:52.000Z","msg":"因為社會對文科生既需求低<br />\n甚至可以話係0需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e80a544b90ed987433ab62f95cc7f775f158bdc","tid":529014,"uid":103616,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53949c8f5f3257e8275cce83f24d1e857f0fc4a7","tid":529014,"uid":7837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"agger"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"一個靠補YY Lam搏grade嘅垃圾dse中文科究竟有乜撚野價值？<br />\n一個中文5**數學拎2嘅吹水垃圾可以順利直入大學<br />\n但係一個數學5**中文2嘅邏輯性學生就只可以retake"},{"pid":"97755302c80115d539e9f84c26d2c75f2ed96f53","tid":529014,"uid":69794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4D0fLisyjBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4D0fLisyjBY&d=n17qn7TJDXoHaR3Der2I%2FP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0abca477\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4D0fLisyjBY</a>"},{"pid":"0212abfa1